data.description: Located in the exclusive community of Cutler Cay, this one-story home features 4 bedrooms and 3-and-a-half bathrooms, offering a spacious and comfortable living space. The high ceilings contribute to an open and airy atmosphere throughout the home. The property includes a heated pool, a cabana bathroom, and a tiki hut covered patio that offers a charming and shaded area for outdoor relaxation. With a living area spanning 2,560 square feet and a lot size of 7,650 square feet, this property offers ample space for both indoor and outdoor activities. The home also boasts two new air conditioning units, new washer and dryer, a 2-car garage, and hurricane panels, that offer protection and peace of mind during severe weather conditions.
